text: "Woman from Tokyo" is a 1973 song by British rock band Deep Purple and taken from their 7th studio album Who Do We Think We Are. It went to number 6 in the Netherlands, number 16 in Germany, number 23 in Belgium, number 60 in the United States and number 62 in Canada. == References == Category:1973 songs Category:Deep Purple songs Category:Hard rock songs Category:Blues rock songs
title: Woman from Tokyo
